WEBVTT

01:43.080 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

01:52.280 --> 01:53.960
I'll go and focus on my great endeavors.

01:55.320 --> 01:56.600
Don't come back too late.

01:56.680 --> 01:57.520
Okay.

01:58.320 --> 01:59.320
Be careful.

01:59.400 --> 02:00.600
- Bye.
- Stay safe.

02:00.680 --> 02:01.520
Bye.

02:19.280 --> 02:20.360
I forgot to tell you.

02:21.440 --> 02:23.200
You should treat Duan Jiaxu to dinner

02:23.280 --> 02:24.520
when you're free.

02:25.920 --> 02:28.080
He's not snitching on you
but concerned about you.

02:29.360 --> 02:30.480
Look.

02:30.560 --> 02:32.600
For the past two years, he kept asking

02:32.680 --> 02:34.240
about your grades and life.

02:34.320 --> 02:35.440
He didn't ask you directly

02:35.520 --> 02:36.720
so you wouldn't feel pressured.

02:38.240 --> 02:39.480
Whenever it was your birthday,

02:40.200 --> 02:41.720
when you got good grades

02:42.360 --> 02:43.720
or during the holidays,

02:43.800 --> 02:45.720
he sent you all kinds of gifts.

02:46.440 --> 02:47.920
He was flat broke himself,

02:48.000 --> 02:49.240
but he still sent you gifts.

02:50.360 --> 02:52.200
Remember, treat him to dinner.

03:01.440 --> 03:05.360
IF YOU'RE EVER OUT SO LATE,
FIND SOMEONE TO ACCOMPANY YOU BACK

03:16.240 --> 03:17.880
I've been ignoring him.

03:18.800 --> 03:20.280
Maybe that wasn't very nice of me.

03:22.600 --> 03:24.400
After all, he hasn't done anything wrong.

03:25.880 --> 03:28.200
From the start, he has been nice to me.

03:32.360 --> 03:34.360
I feel like an ingrate now.

03:35.400 --> 03:36.880
THE DREAM GAMES

03:36.960 --> 03:38.800
Last year, A Dream of Jianghu's expansion,

03:38.880 --> 03:40.800
Fury of Mount Guan hit the market.

03:40.880 --> 03:41.960
The main theme was

03:42.040 --> 03:43.480
an attachment to the homeland

03:43.560 --> 03:44.840
and an underdog hero.

03:44.920 --> 03:45.880
After it went online,

03:45.960 --> 03:47.600
the reception was good.

03:47.680 --> 03:49.520
The players also gave it stellar ratings.

03:49.600 --> 03:50.920
So this year's expansion

03:51.000 --> 03:52.480
is very important to us.

03:52.960 --> 03:54.520
I mentioned this in past meetings.

03:54.600 --> 03:56.800
I hope to see innovation and breakthroughs

03:56.880 --> 03:58.880
in all aspects.

04:00.080 --> 04:02.280
Dawang, how are your preparations?

04:03.120 --> 04:04.280
Everything is set.

04:04.360 --> 04:06.480
Unlike last year's Fury of Mount Guan,

04:06.560 --> 04:08.240
we will be returning to the root

04:08.320 --> 04:10.040
of martial arts fantasy and gameplay.

04:10.120 --> 04:11.520
We will be releasing

04:11.600 --> 04:14.000
unconventional martial arts playstyles.

04:14.520 --> 04:16.360
They will serve as a mechanism

04:16.440 --> 04:18.040
to create more novel stories and content.

04:18.120 --> 04:19.680
I will now show you

04:19.760 --> 04:21.760
the roadmap I came up with.

04:21.839 --> 04:23.160
ROADMAP

04:23.240 --> 04:25.960
I've designed updates to the maps,

04:26.040 --> 04:28.000
characters, instances, and gameplay

04:28.080 --> 04:29.840
around the main quest progression

04:29.920 --> 04:31.720
of the new factions.

04:31.800 --> 04:34.040
I also worked with colleagues
from the Art Department

04:34.120 --> 04:35.440
to come up with a new solution

04:35.520 --> 04:37.000
for the game art style.

04:37.560 --> 04:40.120
I think this theme is pretty good.

04:40.200 --> 04:41.360
It piques my interest.

04:42.360 --> 04:44.160
We should make use of our time

04:44.240 --> 04:45.360
and conduct a player survey.

04:45.880 --> 04:46.880
Now,

04:46.960 --> 04:48.280
it has been over a year

04:48.360 --> 04:51.240
since the last feature technical update.

04:51.840 --> 04:53.280
Does anyone have any new ideas?

04:56.600 --> 04:57.480
Hold on.

04:59.760 --> 05:01.360
I wonder if you still remember

05:01.440 --> 05:04.040
the Celestial Progression System
that I proposed?

05:06.040 --> 05:08.640
It uses an AI algorithm

05:08.720 --> 05:10.240
for self-progression.

05:10.320 --> 05:13.680
It makes the behavioral models
and feedback of our NPCs

05:13.760 --> 05:16.800
a lot more life-like and logical.

05:16.880 --> 05:19.240
It gives players the feeling

05:19.320 --> 05:20.760
that every creation

05:20.840 --> 05:23.040
has its own progression throughout time.

05:23.120 --> 05:25.600
In other words, it recreates

05:25.680 --> 05:27.440
a convincing martial arts world.

05:28.000 --> 05:30.800
But this proposal
had already been rejected.

05:30.880 --> 05:31.840
I don't think

05:31.920 --> 05:33.280
we have the technical prowess

05:33.360 --> 05:34.440
to finish this plan.

05:34.520 --> 05:35.640
That's true.

05:36.200 --> 05:38.520
Therefore, our team came up with a demo

05:38.600 --> 05:39.720
based on pre-research

05:39.800 --> 05:41.160
so we can show you.

05:44.880 --> 05:46.280
You are now looking at the NPC

05:46.360 --> 05:47.720
known as Fang Siming,

05:47.800 --> 05:49.200
whom you're probably familiar with.

05:49.280 --> 05:51.720
It's one of the popular characters
among the players

05:51.800 --> 05:52.800
of A Dream of Jianghu.

05:52.880 --> 05:54.000
I'll now use him

05:54.080 --> 05:55.840
to demonstrate the pre-research effect

05:55.920 --> 05:57.120
of our system.

05:57.200 --> 06:00.360
I will interact with the NPC as a player.

06:00.440 --> 06:03.440
Li Xun, help me with the feedback.

06:04.800 --> 06:06.040
It's starting.

06:12.560 --> 06:14.960
The NPC looks like
he's good at Wuchang chess.

06:15.040 --> 06:16.000
Do you think so?

06:16.080 --> 06:17.360
I bet he's better than Li Xun.

06:19.200 --> 06:21.120
The NPC's reaction was quick.

06:21.200 --> 06:22.040
He's agile.

06:23.880 --> 06:24.800
It seems

06:24.880 --> 06:26.880
that someone has failed to win a drink.

06:26.960 --> 06:28.480
Instead, they owe me a drink.

06:28.560 --> 06:29.800
Li Xun lost!

06:30.840 --> 06:32.080
All right.

06:32.160 --> 06:34.560
I'll pay up next time. Put it on the tab.

06:34.640 --> 06:35.560
Li Xun is backing out.

06:35.640 --> 06:36.520
Fine, I owe you one.

06:36.600 --> 06:39.160
- That's not cool, Li Xun.
- Put it on my tab. I'll pay next time.

06:39.240 --> 06:40.760
A SWORD OF FROST

06:40.840 --> 06:42.200
I'll remember this.

06:43.320 --> 06:46.120
This drink is on me.

06:46.920 --> 06:48.120
Do you care to accept it?

06:49.480 --> 06:51.280
Not bad. He's even flirting with me.

06:53.320 --> 06:55.040
During the design stage,

06:55.120 --> 06:56.600
we set the character's interests

06:56.680 --> 06:57.760
based on the game lore

06:57.840 --> 06:59.280
and the character's back story.

06:59.360 --> 07:01.880
These NPCs are enthused when they interact

07:01.960 --> 07:03.480
with the players.

07:04.240 --> 07:06.000
They can react in a way

07:06.080 --> 07:07.760
that forms a deeper connection

07:07.840 --> 07:09.080
with the players.

07:10.000 --> 07:12.680
But a different player

07:12.760 --> 07:14.800
might not choose to play chess with him.

07:14.880 --> 07:16.920
Is there a way for us to make the NPCs

07:17.000 --> 07:19.960
flexibly handle any situation?

07:20.720 --> 07:22.360
That involves the data

07:22.440 --> 07:23.920
fed to the AI.

07:24.480 --> 07:25.720
Our algorithm

07:25.800 --> 07:28.880
will record every player's
experiences and behaviors

07:28.960 --> 07:30.640
after they log into the game.

07:30.720 --> 07:33.040
So the Celestial Progression System's NPCs

07:33.120 --> 07:36.120
will come up with different reactions
and feedback

07:36.200 --> 07:37.360
to different players.

07:37.440 --> 07:39.280
We could give it a try right now.

07:39.360 --> 07:40.560
We can test it

07:41.080 --> 07:43.480
with a more active account.

07:46.920 --> 07:48.040
Fang Siming.

07:48.120 --> 07:49.160
It has been a while.

07:49.760 --> 07:51.080
Why are you drinking alone?

07:51.160 --> 07:53.040
FOLLOW THE EGRET

07:53.120 --> 07:54.840
I invited the moon to a drink.

07:54.920 --> 07:56.200
My shadow, a second companion.

07:57.480 --> 07:59.600
There's no way
I can't get a drink from him.

07:59.680 --> 08:01.080
Laosan, get it for me.

08:01.160 --> 08:02.040
Okay.

08:02.680 --> 08:04.760
I don't care! I want it!

08:11.680 --> 08:13.040
Bad footwork.

08:13.120 --> 08:15.480
That won't get you a drink, my friend.

08:17.480 --> 08:18.920
Fang Siming is an interesting guy.

08:21.400 --> 08:22.600
Theoretically speaking,

08:22.680 --> 08:25.600
when a large amount of data
is fed to the AI,

08:25.680 --> 08:28.160
it will manifest its own behavior

08:28.240 --> 08:30.520
when the amount of data
reaches a certain level.

08:30.600 --> 08:32.039
This is the part

08:32.120 --> 08:33.840
that AI researchers across the globe

08:33.919 --> 08:35.559
are particularly interested in.

08:36.120 --> 08:38.720
If we can have a technical upgrade

08:38.799 --> 08:40.520
in this regard,

08:40.600 --> 08:42.120
it could be a huge breakthrough

08:42.200 --> 08:43.440
for our game.

08:44.800 --> 08:46.720
But this is just a demo.

08:46.800 --> 08:50.200
If we are to complete
this system successfully,

08:50.280 --> 08:53.360
we need to invest in a lot of NPCs
into the game.

08:54.160 --> 08:57.240
Given our staff
and technical capabilities,

08:57.320 --> 08:59.240
I fear it might not be viable.

08:59.320 --> 09:01.240
If we rush headlong into this,

09:01.320 --> 09:04.240
we might add more risks to the project.

09:04.320 --> 09:06.120
That is a problem.

09:08.880 --> 09:10.320
I need time

09:10.400 --> 09:11.560
to think this over.

09:12.800 --> 09:13.840
Is there anything else

09:13.920 --> 09:15.440
to present in this meeting?

09:15.520 --> 09:16.840
No.

09:16.920 --> 09:18.120
That's all for today.

09:18.200 --> 09:19.040
Okay.

09:19.120 --> 09:20.280
- Okay.
- Okay.

09:20.360 --> 09:21.480
Well done.

09:22.280 --> 09:23.680
You think that will be

09:23.760 --> 09:25.080
a risky move, right?

09:26.120 --> 09:27.680
I think it's a bit risky.

09:28.600 --> 09:29.760
Jiaxu,

09:29.840 --> 09:31.320
there are bound to be problems.

09:31.880 --> 09:33.480
But there will also be solutions.

09:33.560 --> 09:34.800
Solutions outnumber problems.

09:35.640 --> 09:37.160
Yes, Li Xun. Don't worry.

09:38.160 --> 09:39.000
Keep at it.

09:44.240 --> 09:45.520
It's all right.

09:46.080 --> 09:47.000
We've just started.

09:47.080 --> 09:48.040
This is normal.

09:49.000 --> 09:51.160
I'll call for a meeting

09:51.240 --> 09:52.160
with our team.

09:53.000 --> 09:53.880
Sure.

09:54.600 --> 09:55.840
- Keep at it.
- Keep at it.

09:56.400 --> 09:57.240
Your cup.

10:13.560 --> 10:14.880
Jiaxu,

10:15.520 --> 10:17.120
when might you be free?

10:18.480 --> 10:20.040
If it is no trouble,

10:20.120 --> 10:21.640
I would like to treat you to dinner

10:22.480 --> 10:24.080
as a thank you for taking me home.

10:31.120 --> 10:32.920
If you are too busy at the moment,

10:33.000 --> 10:33.920
it is all right.

10:35.520 --> 10:36.880
You can decide the time.

10:40.360 --> 10:42.840
If you are not sure when you are free,

10:44.320 --> 10:46.720
how about next weekend?

10:47.760 --> 10:49.400
I would like to use this chance

10:49.480 --> 10:51.920
to express my gratitude to you.

11:26.480 --> 11:28.280
"When might you be free?

11:29.320 --> 11:30.320
If it is no trouble,

11:30.400 --> 11:32.280
I would like to treat you to dinner

11:32.360 --> 11:34.480
as a thank you for taking me home."

11:41.520 --> 11:42.560
Next weekend?

12:10.120 --> 12:11.000
SANG ZHI

12:11.080 --> 12:12.760
You may decide the time too.

12:13.320 --> 12:14.640
How formal.

12:20.520 --> 12:21.760
VOICE CALL INVITATION FROM JIAXU

12:23.320 --> 12:24.520
JIAXU

12:34.080 --> 12:34.960
Hello, Jiaxu.

12:35.040 --> 12:36.920
I'm free next weekend,

12:37.000 --> 12:39.800
but I'm not sure about the specific time.

12:41.040 --> 12:41.920
It's all right.

12:42.640 --> 12:44.360
We can accommodate your schedule.

12:46.200 --> 12:47.080
Okay.

12:47.160 --> 12:48.080
By the way,

12:48.160 --> 12:50.640
I'll take you
to a phone repair shop as well.

12:52.000 --> 12:53.040
My phone?

12:53.120 --> 12:54.480
Why would I repair it?

12:55.080 --> 12:56.520
Isn't it broken?

12:56.600 --> 12:57.880
It's not.

12:59.960 --> 13:01.640
I thought it must be broken.

13:01.720 --> 13:03.240
Your texts are so formal.

13:05.840 --> 13:07.720
Where did that come from?

13:08.520 --> 13:10.560
You were never so formal with me.

13:10.640 --> 13:12.200
Your words are so polite.

13:14.480 --> 13:15.680
I remember now.

13:16.600 --> 13:18.640
Does this mean

13:18.720 --> 13:20.960
I have a place in your heart?

13:29.600 --> 13:30.440
Jiaxu.

13:31.360 --> 13:32.320
Here's the thing.

13:33.320 --> 13:34.840
My dad told me

13:35.400 --> 13:38.400
to be respectful to anyone older than me

13:38.480 --> 13:39.720
by five years or more.

13:39.800 --> 13:42.000
If I remember correctly,
you're five years older than me.

13:42.560 --> 13:45.600
Your voice sounds young,

13:45.680 --> 13:47.440
but you can't fool anyone.

13:47.520 --> 13:49.400
You're not young anymore.

13:49.480 --> 13:51.160
- So--
- I'm hanging up now. Bye.

13:52.040 --> 13:52.880
Wait.

13:53.400 --> 13:54.280
Hello?

13:59.800 --> 14:02.080
I have something else to tell you.

14:04.120 --> 14:04.960
What is it?

14:08.160 --> 14:09.640
I didn't mean to ignore you

14:09.720 --> 14:12.200
by not replying or calling you back.

14:12.760 --> 14:14.480
I was living on campus.

14:14.560 --> 14:16.200
I didn't have my phone with me.

14:18.440 --> 14:19.280
I know.

14:20.120 --> 14:21.480
Your brother told me that.

14:21.560 --> 14:22.440
You knew?

14:23.320 --> 14:25.080
Then why did you even ask?

14:27.280 --> 14:28.720
Okay, that's it.

14:28.800 --> 14:29.800
That's all for now.

14:29.880 --> 14:30.760
I'm done.

14:30.840 --> 14:31.920
Bye.

15:24.600 --> 15:26.760
CHAPTER NINE, UNDERCURRENT

15:26.840 --> 15:28.680
I CAN'T HELP FALLING IN LOVE

15:34.360 --> 15:35.560
Wait for me!

15:35.640 --> 15:37.160
- Okay.
- Wait for me.

15:37.840 --> 15:38.880
- Hurry up.
- Where is Weiwei?

15:39.760 --> 15:42.480
No idea. She left in a hurry this morning.

15:42.560 --> 15:44.000
Maybe she went to a club meeting.

15:44.080 --> 15:44.960
Who knows?

15:45.480 --> 15:46.400
Sang Zhi.

15:48.440 --> 15:49.480
Jiang Ming.

15:49.560 --> 15:50.560
What are you doing here?

15:51.200 --> 15:52.200
I'm here for Sang Zhi.

15:52.760 --> 15:54.080
Me?

15:54.600 --> 15:55.880
What is it?

16:01.440 --> 16:02.520
Everyone,

16:02.600 --> 16:04.720
look at who's coming.

16:07.200 --> 16:08.720
Ning Wei!

16:09.320 --> 16:10.200
What's going on?

16:10.800 --> 16:12.080
The two of us

16:12.760 --> 16:13.840
are dating.

16:14.400 --> 16:15.920
Yes, we can see that.

16:16.000 --> 16:17.640
Ning Wei.

16:17.720 --> 16:20.200
You don't waste any time, do you?

16:20.880 --> 16:22.440
Are those matching outfits?

16:22.520 --> 16:23.440
Yes.

16:26.720 --> 16:27.960
That's right.

16:28.040 --> 16:30.160
You were here to see Sangsang.

16:32.120 --> 16:33.640
I got premiere tickets last night.

16:33.720 --> 16:34.560
Sang Zhi,

16:34.640 --> 16:36.000
would you like to go with me?

16:38.640 --> 16:40.040
Are you inviting her only?

16:40.520 --> 16:41.360
That's not nice.

16:41.440 --> 16:42.360
Indeed.

16:42.440 --> 16:43.520
Shut it.

16:43.600 --> 16:45.840
If you're all free, feel free to join us.

16:45.920 --> 16:47.160
- We're free.
- Yes.

16:47.240 --> 16:48.400
- Yes.
- Okay.

16:48.480 --> 16:49.720
This Sunday at 8:00 p.m.,

16:49.800 --> 16:50.960
meet at Joy City Cinema.

16:51.040 --> 16:53.120
- Okay.
- Hold on. This Sunday?

16:53.760 --> 16:54.800
I probably can't make it.

16:54.880 --> 16:56.160
I already have plans.

16:56.240 --> 16:57.360
What plans?

16:57.440 --> 16:58.600
No, Sangsang.

16:58.680 --> 16:59.600
Come with us.

16:59.680 --> 17:01.080
- Come on.
- Let's go together.

17:01.160 --> 17:02.880
It has been ages
since we've watched a movie.

17:02.960 --> 17:04.560
If things get awkward

17:04.640 --> 17:05.880
during dinner with him,

17:06.440 --> 17:07.800
I'll have an excuse to leave.

17:09.160 --> 17:10.079
Come on.

17:10.160 --> 17:12.000
We'll go. Sunday, 8:00 p.m.

17:12.079 --> 17:13.119
Great.

17:13.200 --> 17:14.640
- We'll go.
- See you at the cinema.

17:14.720 --> 17:15.960
- Okay.
- See you there.

17:16.520 --> 17:17.960
This is all thank you to you.

17:18.040 --> 17:19.480
- Let's go to class.
- Thank you.

17:22.040 --> 17:23.560
We have a class now.

17:26.440 --> 17:27.400
Let's go.

17:28.160 --> 17:29.080
Come on.

17:29.160 --> 17:30.320
- Bye!
- Chen Qiang!

17:30.400 --> 17:31.280
Let's go.

17:35.600 --> 17:36.480
I'm coming.

17:48.280 --> 17:49.800
Are you Mr. Duan Jiaxu?

17:49.880 --> 17:51.240
- Yes.
- Your parcel.

17:51.320 --> 17:52.640
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

17:57.200 --> 17:59.160
TO DUAN JIAXU, FROM JIANG YING

18:09.400 --> 18:10.760
Did you receive the parcel?

18:10.840 --> 18:12.560
I sent you some tonics

18:12.640 --> 18:14.920
and an essential oil lamp
for stress relief.

18:15.000 --> 18:16.560
Take care of yourself.

18:16.640 --> 18:18.720
Let's have dinner sometime.

18:35.840 --> 18:37.760
JIANG YING, TRANSFER AMOUNT: 8,000 YUAN

18:37.840 --> 18:39.000
WAITING FOR JIANG YING
TO CONFIRM TRANSFER

18:46.600 --> 18:48.800
I've wired the last compensation payment.

18:48.880 --> 18:50.200
Do not contact me again.

19:01.600 --> 19:02.440
Okay.

19:02.520 --> 19:03.720
It makes your skin look fair.

19:05.200 --> 19:06.200
DUAN JIAXU

19:06.280 --> 19:07.880
I'VE WIRED
THE LAST COMPENSATION PAYMENT.

19:07.960 --> 19:09.440
DO NOT CONTACT ME AGAIN.

19:12.000 --> 19:14.080
JIANG YING

19:22.040 --> 19:23.800
Don't contact you again? What do you mean?

19:31.880 --> 19:33.800
JIANG YING

19:42.080 --> 19:43.680
Jiaxu, when will you be free?

19:43.760 --> 19:45.080
Can we meet up?

20:06.560 --> 20:08.360
JIANG YING

20:13.080 --> 20:14.520
Come on, the meeting is starting.

20:14.600 --> 20:15.640
In a moment.

20:24.440 --> 20:26.560
Have you only eaten half an egg today?

20:26.640 --> 20:27.720
You also skipped lunch.

20:28.400 --> 20:30.120
I'll eat it during the meeting.

20:31.600 --> 20:32.760
I'll bring it inside for you.

21:05.040 --> 21:08.040
I've decided to employ Xiaoduan's idea.

21:09.040 --> 21:11.480
The Celestial Progression System
will be the new feature.

21:12.040 --> 21:14.400
However, the new storyline,

21:14.480 --> 21:16.920
instances, factions, and maps

21:17.000 --> 21:19.080
must remain the main focus.

21:19.800 --> 21:21.960
If we are going down this path,

21:22.040 --> 21:23.720
the Planning and Art Departments

21:23.800 --> 21:25.320
will fully cooperate.

21:25.880 --> 21:28.400
But given the current circumstances,

21:28.480 --> 21:31.080
I can't come up with a way
to assign the work

21:31.160 --> 21:34.480
so that everyone
can deliver quality work on time.

21:35.000 --> 21:36.880
Whether the Celestial Progression System

21:36.960 --> 21:39.400
is compatible with most smartphones

21:39.480 --> 21:40.440
is also another problem.

21:40.520 --> 21:42.440
Dawang's concern is justified.

21:43.200 --> 21:44.680
Jiaxu,

21:44.760 --> 21:46.320
do you have a solution for that?

21:48.600 --> 21:51.400
Well, my idea so far

21:51.480 --> 21:53.560
is to take some workload off
other departments

21:53.640 --> 21:55.800
with technical methods.

21:55.880 --> 21:57.560
For example,

21:57.640 --> 21:58.920
manual form filling and whatnot

21:59.000 --> 22:00.680
can be done with technology.

22:02.880 --> 22:04.200
Since it has been decided,

22:04.280 --> 22:05.960
let's give it our best.

22:06.040 --> 22:07.720
We'll solve every problem along the way.

22:07.800 --> 22:08.640
Okay?

22:08.720 --> 22:11.320
If you ever need coordination,

22:11.400 --> 22:12.480
just let us know.

22:13.120 --> 22:16.560
Dawang and Xiaoduan will be in charge

22:16.640 --> 22:17.720
of this new project.

22:20.440 --> 22:21.360
Let's go.

22:26.280 --> 22:27.480
Let's go.

22:27.560 --> 22:28.640
Back to work.

22:28.720 --> 22:29.600
All the best.

23:05.320 --> 23:07.360
Hello, Jiaxu. I'm here.

23:07.440 --> 23:08.600
Where are you?

23:10.760 --> 23:12.200
Sorry, Sang Zhi.

23:12.280 --> 23:14.160
I don't think I can make it tonight.

23:19.400 --> 23:20.720
Are you working overtime?

23:21.680 --> 23:22.680
Yes.

23:22.760 --> 23:24.280
Order something for yourself.

23:24.360 --> 23:25.520
Don't starve.

23:27.920 --> 23:30.760
Your voice sounds off.

23:30.840 --> 23:33.680
Are you not feeling well?

23:34.680 --> 23:35.600
Not at all.

23:40.120 --> 23:41.200
What's wrong?

23:43.360 --> 23:44.840
It's just a little stomach pain.

23:45.480 --> 23:47.080
Maybe it's food poisoning.

23:47.160 --> 23:49.360
It's all right.
I'll just take some medicine.

23:49.440 --> 23:51.680
But shouldn't you go to the hospital?

23:53.240 --> 23:55.120
No need. This is nothing serious.

23:57.120 --> 23:58.520
Why don't you go to the hospital?

23:58.600 --> 24:00.240
Holding off the pain won't make it better.

24:01.320 --> 24:02.640
Where is your office located?

24:04.440 --> 24:05.800
Don't trouble yourself.

24:05.880 --> 24:06.760
I'm all right.

24:08.080 --> 24:09.680
Where is your office located?

24:12.840 --> 24:15.200
Gangbei Complex.

24:17.120 --> 24:18.560
Okay, I'll be right there.

24:21.440 --> 24:22.360
Hello, sir.

24:22.440 --> 24:23.280
Gangbei Complex.

24:36.800 --> 24:37.880
THE DREAM GAMES

24:43.440 --> 24:44.320
Sang Zhi.

24:46.080 --> 24:47.320
What are you doing here?

24:47.400 --> 24:48.880
- You came.
- Are you feeling better?

24:48.960 --> 24:50.800
It's nothing. It's just a stomachache.

24:50.880 --> 24:52.560
Wait here. I'll get a taxi.

24:52.640 --> 24:54.120
I'll take you to the hospital.

24:54.200 --> 24:55.080
Sang Zhi.

24:56.160 --> 24:58.400
- I'll go with you.
- Just wait here for me.

24:58.480 --> 24:59.520
It's all right.

25:00.560 --> 25:01.400
Let me take this.

25:03.800 --> 25:04.640
Lean on me.

25:05.520 --> 25:06.640
- I'm okay.
- Let's go.

25:07.560 --> 25:08.920
Come on. Watch your step.

25:12.200 --> 25:14.440
Are you helping an old man, kiddo?

25:14.520 --> 25:16.600
Can you walk on your own?

25:19.520 --> 25:20.360
I…

25:21.000 --> 25:22.880
- Slowly.
- I'm not saying you're a kid.

25:23.440 --> 25:24.440
It's all right.

25:27.480 --> 25:28.400
Be careful.

25:30.160 --> 25:31.480
Wait here for me.

25:31.560 --> 25:32.400
Okay.

25:32.480 --> 25:33.320
Wait here.

25:37.680 --> 25:38.600
Hey.

25:44.080 --> 25:44.920
Be careful.

25:45.640 --> 25:46.520
Be careful.

25:51.200 --> 25:52.800
I'll book a ride.

25:56.440 --> 25:57.280
What is the address?

26:21.800 --> 26:23.440
I didn't mean to do that.

26:23.520 --> 26:25.080
I didn't mean to either.

26:32.320 --> 26:34.120
Jiaxu, get in the car.

26:39.360 --> 26:44.760
HAIXIA TAXI

26:44.840 --> 26:45.720
Watch out.

26:45.800 --> 26:46.800
- I'm fine.
- Mind your head.

26:47.680 --> 26:48.520
Hello.

26:50.480 --> 26:51.960
- Hello.
- Hello.

26:54.160 --> 26:56.320
Is he drunk or something?

26:56.920 --> 26:58.960
- No.
- Is he going to throw up?

26:59.040 --> 27:00.440
No, sir.

27:00.520 --> 27:02.440
Sir, I won't throw up.

27:02.520 --> 27:03.400
I can hang in there.

27:03.480 --> 27:05.480
No, let me say this first.

27:05.560 --> 27:07.000
If you throw up in the car,

27:07.080 --> 27:08.040
you pay 200 yuan.

27:08.120 --> 27:09.040
Okay?

27:09.120 --> 27:10.400
He won't throw up.

27:10.480 --> 27:11.600
He has stomach pains.

27:11.680 --> 27:12.560
Go to the hospital.

27:12.640 --> 27:13.920
Take us to the hospital.

27:14.000 --> 27:15.880
- Okay.
- Sir, please hurry.

27:15.960 --> 27:16.800
Okay.

27:30.920 --> 27:31.880
OUTPATIENT BUILDING

27:31.960 --> 27:33.480
Judging by the ultrasound,

27:33.560 --> 27:34.560
it's acute appendicitis.

27:34.640 --> 27:36.760
And you waited to come in.

27:36.840 --> 27:38.720
Had you come any later,
it would've ruptured.

27:38.800 --> 27:40.080
What do we do now?

27:40.160 --> 27:41.360
One is conservative therapy.

27:41.440 --> 27:43.520
- We admit you and ease the inflammation.
- I see.

27:43.600 --> 27:44.480
The other method

27:44.560 --> 27:45.840
is going straight to surgery.

27:46.400 --> 27:48.040
- Then--
- Do the surgery.

27:48.120 --> 27:49.160
Okay.

27:51.680 --> 27:52.760
It will be all right.

28:01.760 --> 28:02.680
Sang Zhi.

28:04.840 --> 28:06.840
It's late. Head back to campus.

28:07.360 --> 28:09.120
It will be unsafe later.

28:09.200 --> 28:10.840
I'll wait for you outside.

28:12.720 --> 28:14.120
It's not a major surgery.

28:14.840 --> 28:16.200
- It's okay.
- I'll wait for you.

28:17.240 --> 28:18.280
The surgery will take--

28:18.360 --> 28:19.360
Stop talking.

28:20.120 --> 28:22.640
Go and get yourself something to eat.

28:42.840 --> 28:45.480
Had we not had plans for dinner today,

28:46.480 --> 28:48.360
he would have just held it off

28:49.480 --> 28:50.880
and never come to the hospital.

29:01.120 --> 29:02.920
"Avoid overworking.

29:04.240 --> 29:05.080
Avoid alcohol."

29:05.160 --> 29:06.040
MOM

29:11.280 --> 29:12.160
Hello, Mom.

29:12.800 --> 29:13.880
Hello, Zhizhi.

29:15.400 --> 29:17.760
It's past ten. Why haven't you called me?

29:18.520 --> 29:19.520
Are you at the dorm

29:19.600 --> 29:20.920
or hanging out with friends?

29:21.480 --> 29:22.400
No.

29:24.040 --> 29:27.320
Do you remember Sang Yan's classmate?

29:27.400 --> 29:29.720
He gave me physics lessons

29:29.800 --> 29:31.240
when I was in high school.

29:31.320 --> 29:32.200
Duan Jiaxu.

29:33.480 --> 29:35.200
I remember. Xiaoduan, right?

29:37.880 --> 29:40.080
We had plans to have dinner together,

29:40.160 --> 29:42.000
but he suddenly fell ill,

29:42.080 --> 29:43.920
so I took him to the hospital.

29:44.000 --> 29:45.040
Is he sick?

29:45.760 --> 29:46.640
What is it?

29:46.720 --> 29:47.760
Is it serious?

29:48.240 --> 29:49.760
Acute appendicitis.

29:49.840 --> 29:51.400
He's in surgery now.

29:55.160 --> 29:56.640
Poor thing.

29:56.720 --> 29:58.240
He doesn't have a family.

29:59.640 --> 30:01.720
What do you mean?

30:01.800 --> 30:03.640
His home is in Yihe, isn't it?

30:06.600 --> 30:09.000
I never told you about his background.

30:11.920 --> 30:12.800
Mr. Sang.

30:14.320 --> 30:15.640
There are 6,000 yuan left

30:15.720 --> 30:16.560
after the funeral.

30:16.640 --> 30:18.200
I'm returning this to you.

30:18.280 --> 30:20.160
I'll pay you the remaining balance

30:20.240 --> 30:21.280
after I get a job.

30:21.360 --> 30:24.000
Xiaoduan, keep the money for yourself.

30:24.080 --> 30:25.320
Don't rush to repay us.

30:25.400 --> 30:28.000
No, you have to take the money.

30:28.080 --> 30:28.920
Keep it.

30:30.680 --> 30:31.880
Keep the money and use it.

30:32.600 --> 30:33.720
You've been through a lot.

30:37.640 --> 30:38.760
I'm all right.

30:38.840 --> 30:40.200
It was nothing.

30:43.840 --> 30:44.800
Mr. and Mrs. Sang,

30:44.880 --> 30:47.440
you should take the money.

30:48.120 --> 30:50.200
There are other things I must attend to.

30:50.280 --> 30:51.280
I should get going.

30:52.200 --> 30:53.040
Thank you for your time.

30:54.880 --> 30:55.800
Xiaoduan.

30:56.680 --> 30:58.280
Dinner is ready.

30:58.360 --> 30:59.280
Eat before you go.

31:09.600 --> 31:11.040
No, thank you, Mrs. Sang.

31:11.120 --> 31:12.000
Thank you

31:12.960 --> 31:15.480
for looking after me during this time.

31:15.960 --> 31:17.080
Without you…

31:19.000 --> 31:20.000
Thank you so much.

31:20.080 --> 31:21.360
You don't have to do this, child.

31:23.520 --> 31:24.400
Stand up.

31:26.160 --> 31:27.240
I'm going to go.

31:36.240 --> 31:37.800
The poor child.

31:37.880 --> 31:40.520
He's just a college freshman
about 18 years old.

31:41.240 --> 31:42.960
Who knows what else he will face?

31:43.440 --> 31:46.240
Sang Yan, look after him in school.

31:47.480 --> 31:48.320
Okay.

31:49.480 --> 31:51.040
In less than six months,

31:51.120 --> 31:52.600
he paid us back the rest of the sum.

31:54.160 --> 31:55.360
But his mom

31:56.840 --> 31:58.080
had passed away.

32:01.440 --> 32:02.320
Zhizhi.

32:03.520 --> 32:05.920
Don't stay out too late.

32:06.800 --> 32:08.240
Be safe on the way back.

32:12.360 --> 32:13.400
I'm hanging up now.

32:31.800 --> 32:33.400
He has to be hospitalized for seven days.

32:33.480 --> 32:35.440
He can't have solid food for now.

32:35.520 --> 32:37.480
He has to be on a liquid diet for a week.

32:37.560 --> 32:39.800
Should anything come up, just let us know.

32:41.200 --> 32:42.080
Thank you.

32:42.160 --> 32:43.040
Thank you.

32:55.520 --> 32:56.400
Jiaxu.

32:57.040 --> 32:58.320
I asked the nurses.

32:58.880 --> 33:00.200
They said these are what you need

33:00.280 --> 33:01.560
while you're in the hospital.

33:02.120 --> 33:04.000
But if you need anything else,

33:04.080 --> 33:05.240
let me know.

33:05.320 --> 33:06.840
I'll get it for you.

33:07.440 --> 33:08.640
Thank you, Sang Zhi.

33:09.680 --> 33:10.800
It's getting late.

33:10.880 --> 33:12.440
You should head back to campus.

33:14.480 --> 33:17.680
Get a taxi when you leave.

33:17.760 --> 33:19.800
Send the plate number to me.

33:20.560 --> 33:22.400
Let me know when you reach the dorm.

33:22.480 --> 33:23.320
Okay?

33:23.400 --> 33:24.360
Jiaxu.

33:25.600 --> 33:26.800
I'm not a kid anymore.

33:26.880 --> 33:27.800
Don't worry about me.

33:27.880 --> 33:29.120
I know what to do.

33:30.560 --> 33:31.480
Okay.

33:31.560 --> 33:32.520
Leave the things here.

33:32.600 --> 33:33.800
I'll put them away later.

33:39.400 --> 33:40.440
Did the wound hurt?

33:41.800 --> 33:43.000
I got anesthetics,

33:43.560 --> 33:44.800
so it doesn't hurt at all.

33:44.880 --> 33:45.760
I don't feel a thing.

33:46.280 --> 33:47.480
Don't worry.

33:47.560 --> 33:48.800
Go back now.

33:51.480 --> 33:53.000
I'll visit you tomorrow.

33:53.760 --> 33:55.600
Come when you don't have classes.

33:56.120 --> 33:57.760
I'm an adult.

33:57.840 --> 33:59.720
Don't trouble yourself for me.

34:00.400 --> 34:01.720
I'll be fine. Go on.

34:55.440 --> 34:56.840
Is she upset?

35:19.840 --> 35:22.440
She probably minds that.

35:38.600 --> 35:39.520
Hello?

35:41.600 --> 35:42.600
Hello, buddy.

35:43.440 --> 35:45.000
I heard you got your appendix cut out.

35:45.720 --> 35:46.640
How does that feel?

35:48.440 --> 35:50.680
Not bad. Would you like to try it?

35:52.240 --> 35:53.320
No, thank you.

35:53.400 --> 35:55.040
But I heard my sister took you there.

35:55.800 --> 35:56.680
Yes.

35:57.440 --> 35:59.440
Did you have to trouble her
for such a small problem?

35:59.520 --> 36:01.240
Couldn't you go to the hospital yourself?

36:01.320 --> 36:03.280
Did you call just to tell me that?

36:03.920 --> 36:06.520
No, I had dinner with my parents.

36:06.600 --> 36:08.040
They told me you were sick,

36:08.120 --> 36:09.440
so I called to celebrate.

36:10.160 --> 36:11.840
If there's nothing else, I'm hanging up.

36:11.920 --> 36:13.040
I'll carry on with my game.

36:15.080 --> 36:16.000
Hold on.

36:16.720 --> 36:18.400
I want to tell you something.

36:19.440 --> 36:20.800
What is it?

36:23.280 --> 36:24.920
Forget it. It's nothing important.

36:26.320 --> 36:27.920
Buddy, can you not do this every time?

36:28.000 --> 36:30.800
Just spill it like a real man!

36:31.400 --> 36:32.760
It's nothing. Bye.

36:34.240 --> 36:35.280
Hey!

36:50.160 --> 36:51.520
Why did you come back?

36:56.280 --> 36:57.200
Jiaxu.

36:58.080 --> 36:59.280
I gave it some thought.

37:01.160 --> 37:03.440
I should stay and look after you.

37:04.600 --> 37:07.280
If I were to fall sick
and had no one by my side,

37:08.040 --> 37:09.680
you would do the same for me.

37:10.640 --> 37:11.680
Right?

37:24.160 --> 37:25.320
Did you have dinner?

37:30.080 --> 37:30.960
I brought dinner.

37:40.800 --> 37:42.920
You haven't eaten.
Are you only having bread?

37:43.800 --> 37:44.800
Forget this.

37:44.880 --> 37:45.880
I'll order takeouts.

37:46.840 --> 37:48.400
Don't do that. I'm not hungry.

37:48.960 --> 37:50.480
You haven't eaten all day.

37:50.560 --> 37:51.840
You must be starving.

37:51.920 --> 37:52.920
I'm not hungry at all.

37:53.680 --> 37:55.840
If I were, I would get something to eat.

37:56.600 --> 37:57.720
I'm not a kid anymore.

37:58.360 --> 38:00.200
I don't need you to worry.

38:39.640 --> 38:41.440
She is stuffed like a pufferfish again.

38:58.760 --> 39:00.120
Jiaxu, what's so funny?

39:01.440 --> 39:02.720
Nothing.

39:11.120 --> 39:11.960
Where are you going?

39:12.800 --> 39:14.440
I'm going to freshen up.

39:15.520 --> 39:16.760
Go on.

39:49.760 --> 39:51.320
He can't get out of bed today.

39:52.160 --> 39:53.440
So he can't clean himself.

39:54.600 --> 39:56.000
Maybe I should help him wipe…

40:11.040 --> 40:12.280
Jiaxu.

40:12.360 --> 40:14.440
The doctor said you can't shower today.

40:14.520 --> 40:15.960
Do you want to wipe your face?

40:16.040 --> 40:17.000
Sure.

40:18.880 --> 40:19.800
I can help you.

40:20.400 --> 40:21.720
It's okay. I'll manage.

40:21.800 --> 40:23.800
What if you open up your wound?

40:25.600 --> 40:27.520
You'll have to spend even more days here.

40:30.440 --> 40:31.320
All right.

42:05.600 --> 42:07.760
I don't have a nice outfit
to wear to the movie!

42:08.400 --> 42:09.760
It's just across from campus.

42:09.840 --> 42:11.280
You still spent ages on your makeup.

42:11.360 --> 42:12.200
Let's go.

42:12.280 --> 42:13.800
Of course it's necessary!

42:13.880 --> 42:15.440
Girls want to look their best

42:15.520 --> 42:17.600
when meeting someone they like.

42:17.680 --> 42:19.000
You don't get it.

42:19.080 --> 42:20.320
Okay, I don't get it.

42:20.400 --> 42:22.160
Ning Wei is a love expert.

42:22.240 --> 42:23.400
Come on.

42:25.240 --> 42:26.520
Wait for me.

42:26.600 --> 42:28.440
You look good enough. Let's go.

42:28.520 --> 42:30.000
Just wait for a second!

42:30.080 --> 42:31.160
Hurry up.

42:31.240 --> 42:32.440
I know. Stop rushing me.

42:32.520 --> 42:33.480
Bye, Sangsang.

42:33.560 --> 42:34.400
Bye.

42:35.000 --> 42:35.920
Hurry up!

42:36.400 --> 42:37.240
I'll be right there.

42:37.320 --> 42:38.560
We're leaving. Bye!

42:38.640 --> 42:39.760
- Hurry up!
- See you later.

42:40.320 --> 42:41.600
Bye!

42:58.400 --> 42:59.520
It has been so long.

42:59.600 --> 43:01.240
You've learned how to put on makeup.

43:01.320 --> 43:02.760
You're indeed different from before.
